Package: rreporttools
Type: Package
Title: A small set of tools for performing common reporting tasks
Version: 0.1
Date: 2013-11-07
Author: Michael Sachs <michael.sachs@nih.gov>
Maintainer: Michael Sachs <michael.sachs@nih.gov>
Description: rreporttools provides a small set of functions to make our lives
    easier at the Division of Statistical Analysis and Reporting. These
    functions extend several packages. We extend data.table and plyr to include
    totals and subtotals. We also extend xlsx to make formatting
    almost completely automatic.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.1),
    knitr,
    xlsx,
    data.table,
    plyr,
    RJDBC,
    reshape2,
    shiny
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Collate:
    'rreporttools-DTplyWithTotals.R'
    'rreporttools-authorShiny.R'
    'rreporttools-convertSASQuery.R'
    'rreporttools-ddplyWithTotals.R'
    'rreporttools-formatDataFrame.R'
    'rreporttools-formatTotals.R'
    'rreporttools-mydbGetQuery.R'
    'rreporttools-package.R'
